<div dir="ltr">Dear Thomas,<div style>thank you again.</div><div style><br></div><div style>Symlink in /usr/lib64 is not enough, I have symlinked also in /home/stefano/opt/mpi/openmpi/1.6.4/intel/lib and, as expected, not only libimf.so but also ibirng.so and libintlc.so.5 are necessary.</div>
